    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演<strong>Coral</strong>，她是一次殖民未知星球失败任务中的最后幸存者之一，探索母舰<strong>Crystal Mountain</strong>的残骸。这艘船如今已变成一片废墟，笼罩在闪烁的灯光、金属回音和令人不安的声音中。但你并不孤单：外星生物——黑色黏稠的怪物，带着一只红色的眼睛——在废墟中游荡。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有明确的任务指引，也没有箭头告诉你该往哪里走。你的好奇心将引导你：自由探索，寻找隐藏在游戏世界中的线索。你需要收集痕迹，拼凑出过去的碎片，揭示真相。表象往往虚假：每一次发现都可能揭示意想不到的联系，解锁那些等待你发现的秘密。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 垂直互通区域的非线性探索<br></li><li> 快速且富有节奏感的战斗系统<br></li><li> 拥有可解锁技能与升级内容的RPG元素<br></li><li> 紧张激烈且令人难忘的Boss战<br></li><li> 大量隐藏的秘密等待发现</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
